{"tid":980824,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"賭波最重要係心態 希望大家贏多啲","createTime":"2019-01-13T18:53:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-15T13:22:39.000Z","uid":231116,"like":10,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"1d191e62c961c09992f32fbb144bbccf0261f84e","tid":980824,"uid":231116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T18:53:22.000Z","msg":"有感而發<br />\n最近身邊有個兄弟賭波經歷完大起大落<br />\n我知佢心情呢一刻一定好複雜<br />\n同時知佢有睇開連登<br />\n所以平時用開高登嘅我開左個連登ac<br />\n希望比大家有賭波嘅戰友睇下<br />\n<br />\n我認為賭波係一件好撚開心嘅事<br />\n當你中左個刻 可以證明到自己有眼光同埋運氣<br />\n但其實當中運氣所佔嘅成份係大好多<br />\n賭波唔同買股票<br />\n希望大家可以用一個正確嘅心態去賭波<br />\n輸錢皆因贏錢起<br />\n最緊要唔好因為賭波影響生活<br />\n<br />\n希望大家贏多啲<br />\n<br />\n最後 <br />\n馬賽 -0.5/-1"},{"pid":"7c4a23d8fd98a7fbd56ba9faeb4f67db7ef92264","tid":980824,"uid":141543,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T18:54:31.000Z","msg":"ok allin 摩納哥"},{"pid":"bf74be989aaeae79ad22bbdb652912127e9afac7","tid":980824,"uid":231116,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"7c4a23d8fd98a7fbd56ba9faeb4f67db7ef92264","tid":980824,"uid":141543,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T18:54:31.000Z","msg":"ok allin 摩納哥"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T18:55:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 比下面好冇"},{"pid":"61a8c93a76185138b2e583464614af69abdca991","tid":980824,"uid":123787,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T18:56:52.000Z","msg":"買波唔同買股票?<br />\n樓主可唔可以講下買波要有咩心態，買股票又要有咩心態？"},{"pid":"7c9d1344394788a5db32eb888215040eaaae252b","tid":980824,"uid":31542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T18:57:39.000Z","msg":"對左 要左亨利<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4333cc9183c2be868460bb050a96eda5840c527c","tid":980824,"uid":231116,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid